15
00:02:09,367 --> 00:02:12,567
Gosh, now what...

16
00:02:12,567 --> 00:02:14,967
It's nothing.

17
00:02:14,967 --> 00:02:18,667
Ran, I'll bet you're scared.

18
00:02:18,667 --> 00:02:20,467
That there's a mountain monster

19
00:02:20,467 --> 00:02:22,367
