28
00:02:46,367 --> 00:02:50,467
Pops, which means the car we just saw...

29
00:02:50,467 --> 00:02:51,667
Yeah.

30
00:02:51,667 --> 00:02:54,067
It could've been an apparition.

31
00:02:59,367 --> 00:03:05,167
"The Lucky Cigar Case (Part 1)"

32
00:03:05,867 --> 00:03:08,267
Hey, hey, let's not...

33
00:03:08,267 --> 00:03:10,267
Don't worry.

34
00:03:10,267 --> 00:03:11,867
You saw the sign, didn't you?

35
00:03:11,867 --> 00:03:15,667
It's a study facility for a legitimate company.

36
00:03:15,667 --> 00:03:16,667
The people of the company

37
00:03:16,667 --> 00:03:18,667
would never be in a place like this at this time!

38
00:03:18,667 --> 00:03:21,567
I'm sure the car we just saw is a robber's car or something.

39
00:03:21,567 --> 00:03:22,867
What the...

40
00:03:22,867 --> 00:03:24,967
I'll go first and check things out!

41
00:03:24,967 --> 00:03:26,667
Be careful!

42
00:03:29,767 --> 00:03:31,167
Oh, it's a car.

43
00:03:35,367 --> 00:03:37,367
It still warm.

44
00:03:37,367 --> 00:03:39,667
It's a cute car.

45
00:03:39,667 --> 00:03:40,867
What a relief!

46
00:03:40,867 --> 00:03:43,367
Bad people don't ride cars like this, do they?

47
00:03:43,367 --> 00:03:46,767
There seems to be a lot of other cars. See.

48
00:03:49,167 --> 00:03:51,367
This one is warmer!

49
00:03:51,367 --> 00:03:54,867
The car that came in here just a while ago is probably this car!

50
00:03:57,067 --> 00:04:00,767
This car is still warm too.

51
00:04:00,767 --> 00:04:02,167
Which means...

52
00:04:02,167 --> 00:04:05,467
There are people here for sure!

53
00:04:05,467 --> 00:04:06,867
-Let's go! -Okay!

54
00:04:12,967 --> 00:04:16,267
Kuron Health Equipment Corporation.

55
00:04:16,267 --> 00:04:18,167
I've never heard of them.

56
00:04:20,167 --> 00:04:22,167
You two, mind your manners.

57
00:04:22,167 --> 00:04:23,367
Yes, sir!

58
00:04:25,267 --> 00:04:26,867
Hello!

59
00:04:26,867 --> 00:04:29,367
Is anyone in?

60
00:04:32,067 --> 00:04:34,967
They couldn't be sleeping at this hour yet, could they...

61
00:04:39,167 --> 00:04:40,167
What it is?

62
00:04:40,867 --> 00:04:42,967
I'm sorry to be intruding on you at this hour,

63
00:04:42,967 --> 00:04:46,067
but our car broke down nearby.

64
00:04:47,967 --> 00:04:51,567
So, you see, we're stalled in this fog,

65
00:04:51,567 --> 00:04:54,367
so we would like to ask you for some help.

66
00:04:54,367 --> 00:04:56,067
Please go find someone else to help you,

67
00:04:56,067 --> 00:04:58,167
because I'm going to get busy from now.

68
00:04:58,167 --> 00:05:00,767
Wait!

69
00:05:00,767 --> 00:05:03,767
Please at least lend us your phone! Please!

70
00:05:06,667 --> 00:05:08,067
Please wait!

71
00:05:08,067 --> 00:05:09,267
Wait.

72
00:05:09,267 --> 00:05:11,367
Hey!

73
00:05:11,367 --> 00:05:13,567
What a guy.

74
00:05:13,567 --> 00:05:16,367
I promise that if I die, I'll come and haunt you!

75
00:05:16,367 --> 00:05:18,467
Darn.

76
00:05:18,467 --> 00:05:20,767
I guess we'll just have to go back to the car.

77
00:05:20,767 --> 00:05:22,567
It's cold.

78
00:05:24,067 --> 00:05:25,967
You seem to be in trouble.

79
00:05:25,967 --> 00:05:27,367
Please do come in.

80
00:05:27,367 --> 00:05:29,267
Wow, is it okay?

81
00:05:29,267 --> 00:05:31,567
Thank you so very much!

82
00:05:33,867 --> 00:05:35,867
What a fix, eh.

83
00:05:35,867 --> 00:05:38,367
This is a study facility for the company

84
00:05:38,367 --> 00:05:40,667
that there's usually no one here.

85
00:05:42,067 --> 00:05:44,167
The phone's over there.

86
00:05:44,167 --> 00:05:46,767
Thank you.

87
00:05:46,767 --> 00:05:48,267
Are you sure it's okay?

88
00:05:48,267 --> 00:05:50,567
What if they're spies?

89
00:05:50,567 --> 00:05:52,267
Talk about push over,

90
00:05:52,267 --> 00:05:54,467
or rather is it that you have a lot of elbow room

91
00:05:54,467 --> 00:05:56,167
because you're in the 1st development section?

92
00:05:56,167 --> 00:05:58,067
I heard you all!

93
00:05:58,067 --> 00:05:59,067
Oh, president.

94
00:05:59,067 --> 00:06:01,167
Just what are you guys doing?

95
00:06:03,067 --> 00:06:04,967
We're sorry to be intruding on you,

96
00:06:04,967 --> 00:06:07,967
but we're not suspicious people.

97
00:06:07,967 --> 00:06:13,367
I am a private detective and my name is Kogoro Mouri.

98
00:06:13,367 --> 00:06:17,867
Mouri, you mean that famous "Sleeping Mouri"?

99
00:06:17,867 --> 00:06:19,767
Yes, well...

100
00:06:19,767 --> 00:06:22,067
this is my daughter Ran,

101
00:06:22,067 --> 00:06:25,467
and the little one there is Conan.

102
00:06:25,467 --> 00:06:27,167
Oh my,

103
00:06:27,167 --> 00:06:28,867
I am very honored to be able meet you.

104
00:06:28,867 --> 00:06:34,167
I am the president of Kuron Health Equipment Corporation, Umetani.

105
00:06:34,167 --> 00:06:37,167
Please make yourselves at home here.

106
00:06:37,167 --> 00:06:38,667
Oh, that's right!

107
00:06:38,667 --> 00:06:41,467
Mr. Mouri, please become a monitor for us!

108
00:06:41,467 --> 00:06:43,267
How about it?

109
00:06:43,267 --> 00:06:46,567
We having an in-company competition on a relax sheet,

110
00:06:46,567 --> 00:06:48,367
and we would appreciate it if you could give us

111
00:06:48,367 --> 00:06:50,267
your unbiased opinion how you feel about it.

112
00:06:50,267 --> 00:06:52,167
Oh...

113
00:07:00,467 --> 00:07:02,567
There, right there.

114
00:07:04,967 --> 00:07:06,967
This is just great.

115
00:07:06,967 --> 00:07:09,367
It feels so good!

116
00:07:09,367 --> 00:07:13,267
Dad, you're so embarrassing.

117
00:07:14,367 --> 00:07:18,967
I've never experienced a great massage chair like this!

118
00:07:18,967 --> 00:07:21,867
It fits right into the vital spot.

119
00:07:21,867 --> 00:07:24,467
Yes, the combination of the softness of tanned hide

120
00:07:24,467 --> 00:07:26,967
and the combination of artificial leather for durability

121
00:07:26,967 --> 00:07:28,867
makes for a sensation of perfect fit.

122
00:07:28,867 --> 00:07:31,267
Just as expected of the 1st development section!

123
00:07:31,267 --> 00:07:33,167
Well done, Nakano!

124
00:07:33,667 --> 00:07:34,867
But, president.

125
00:07:34,867 --> 00:07:38,267
That artificial leather you take pride in is made in Italy!

126
00:07:38,267 --> 00:07:39,467
Moreover, for the massager part,

127
00:07:39,467 --> 00:07:42,667
high grade silicone rubber is lavishly used!

128
00:07:42,667 --> 00:07:45,867
Therefore, the production cost is too high.

129
00:07:45,867 --> 00:07:48,567
What? What is the meaning of this, Nakano?

130
00:07:48,567 --> 00:07:50,267
The original parts of the basic components such as the rollers,

131
00:07:50,267 --> 00:07:53,267
are of the same product line as what we've used so far,

132
00:07:53,267 --> 00:07:54,867
so as far as that's concerned, the cost is...

133
00:07:54,867 --> 00:07:56,767
You idiot!

134
00:07:56,767 --> 00:07:59,367
Never mind durability!

135
00:07:59,367 --> 00:08:02,167
But, even if we don't make much profit,

136
00:08:02,167 --> 00:08:04,767
so long as we produce good items to our customers,

137
00:08:04,767 --> 00:08:05,967
eventually...

138
00:08:05,967 --> 00:08:08,167
Eventually is not what we're after!

139
00:08:08,167 --> 00:08:10,567
Make profit for me right this minute!

140
00:08:10,567 --> 00:08:12,467
Rather, what I mean is,

141
00:08:12,467 --> 00:08:15,167
if we don't keep dishing out new products,

142
00:08:15,167 --> 00:08:18,067
the customers will give up on us.

143
00:08:18,967 --> 00:08:20,967
Next!

144
00:08:21,867 --> 00:08:24,267
That president is kind of scary, isn't he?

145
00:08:24,267 --> 00:08:25,367
Yeah.

146
00:08:25,367 --> 00:08:29,167
Next for the 2nd development section's Ecstasy One.

147
00:08:29,167 --> 00:08:33,367
This product is made for the younger generation.

148
00:08:33,367 --> 00:08:34,967
Please take a look.

149
00:08:34,967 --> 00:08:36,567
This seat is a cover-type seat.

150
00:08:36,567 --> 00:08:38,967
There are 7 color variations and the color of the customer's choice

151
00:08:38,967 --> 00:08:41,767
can be chosen to meet any type of interior.

152
00:08:41,767 --> 00:08:45,567
The back part of the seat can be reclined to any angle,

153
00:08:45,567 --> 00:08:49,967
and it can also be used in the living room as a sofa.

154
00:08:49,967 --> 00:08:51,267
I see,

155
00:08:51,267 --> 00:08:54,067
it sure seems to be great for a young person's room!

156
00:08:54,067 --> 00:08:56,467
You move this device using the remote controller

157
00:08:56,467 --> 00:08:58,567
that is in the side pocket.

158
00:08:58,567 --> 00:09:01,367
First, let's start with full body massage...

159
00:09:04,767 --> 00:09:07,167
Are you sleepy, Conan?

160
00:09:10,167 --> 00:09:12,867
Stop it already.

161
00:09:12,867 --> 00:09:15,067
What on earth is this?

162
00:09:15,067 --> 00:09:16,367
It's made for young people

163
00:09:16,367 --> 00:09:19,167
so maybe it's too strong for you, Mr. Mouri?

164
00:09:19,167 --> 00:09:21,867
I'll switch it to weak sleep mode.

165
00:09:21,867 --> 00:09:23,367
No thanks!

166
00:09:23,367 --> 00:09:24,767
Relieve my tiredness, my foot!

167
00:09:24,767 --> 00:09:27,167
My whole body feels as if it's going to fall apart!

168
00:09:27,167 --> 00:09:28,767
But...

169
00:09:28,767 --> 00:09:30,867
Kasahara! That's enough.

170
00:09:30,867 --> 00:09:34,267
-Oh, well... -Next! Hiramatsu!

171
00:09:34,267 --> 00:09:36,067
Yes.

172
00:09:37,567 --> 00:09:39,467
Hey, hey, what's this?

173
00:09:39,467 --> 00:09:43,167
Are you going to beat up some monster?

174
00:09:43,167 --> 00:09:44,167
Come to think of it,

175
00:09:44,167 --> 00:09:47,367
my child has a toy that looks something like this.

176
00:09:47,367 --> 00:09:50,567
Really, it looks like some robot animation.

177
00:09:50,567 --> 00:09:53,367
Well, take a look at it, please.

178
00:09:54,867 --> 00:09:58,567
Oh, yes, right there!

179
00:09:58,567 --> 00:10:00,867
Right, just great, right there!

180
00:10:00,867 --> 00:10:02,467
Dad?

181
00:10:02,467 --> 00:10:05,567
How does this thing know just where I want to be massaged?

182
00:10:05,567 --> 00:10:07,767
Right! That's exactly what the main feature

183
00:10:07,767 --> 00:10:10,767
