184
00:10:10,767 --> 00:10:13,467
A micro sensor detects the part of your body that is stiff

185
00:10:13,467 --> 00:10:16,767
and massages with the exact strength needed.

186
00:10:16,767 --> 00:10:18,967
Sounds like a great function,

187
00:10:18,967 --> 00:10:21,567
but I'll bet the cost is really high.

188
00:10:21,567 --> 00:10:24,967
No, the only thing new is the program,

189
00:10:24,967 --> 00:10:28,367
and the rest involves diverting what was being used till now,

190
00:10:28,367 --> 00:10:33,367
so I think the cost is less than half of what your cost is!

191
00:10:33,367 --> 00:10:35,567
Besides, with a function as good as that,

192
00:10:35,567 --> 00:10:38,767
it'll probably sell even if the price is a bit high.

193
00:10:38,767 --> 00:10:40,367
Yes.

194
00:10:40,367 --> 00:10:45,367
So! I'll think over which machine I'll sell

195
00:10:45,367 --> 00:10:47,767
while taking a smoke.

196
00:10:47,767 --> 00:10:49,267
Mr. Mouri, do make yourself at home too!

197
00:10:49,267 --> 00:10:53,667
Thank you. I don't want to come out just yet.

198
00:10:55,467 --> 00:10:59,367
Well, it feels so good, I feel like falling asleep.

199
00:10:59,367 --> 00:11:02,967
Dad, you're interfering everybody with their work!

200
00:11:02,967 --> 00:11:06,767
It's okay, because it seems he's already decided so...

201
00:11:06,767 --> 00:11:08,467
I'm sorry.

202
00:11:08,467 --> 00:11:11,567
Things are moving really fast today, don't you think?

203
00:11:11,567 --> 00:11:13,467
It seems like the rumor about behind the scenes negotiations

204
00:11:13,467 --> 00:11:15,567
was true after all.

205
00:11:15,567 --> 00:11:18,367
It's probably because Mr. Mouri played monitor for us.

206
00:11:18,367 --> 00:11:20,467
President didn't even have to think about it,

207
00:11:20,467 --> 00:11:22,767
but I guess he just wanted to emphasize his importance.

208
00:11:22,767 --> 00:11:24,467
I get it!

209
00:11:24,467 --> 00:11:27,467
Maybe the rumor about the development section

210
00:11:27,467 --> 00:11:30,267
going to be downsized is true!

211
00:11:30,267 --> 00:11:32,267
Maybe he's thinking over which development section

212
00:11:32,267 --> 00:11:34,467
to shut down now.

213
00:11:35,367 --> 00:11:37,867
By the way, Mr. Kasahara, your seat

214
00:11:37,867 --> 00:11:41,467
pushes at the vital points even if it isn't moving.

215
00:11:41,467 --> 00:11:42,667
It's so lumpy!

216
00:11:42,667 --> 00:11:44,867
What? How dare you...

217
00:11:44,867 --> 00:11:47,667
Please calm down, Mr. Kasahara!

218
00:11:47,667 --> 00:11:50,267
Thank you everyone!

219
00:11:50,267 --> 00:11:52,867
May you all work together in peace.

220
00:11:52,867 --> 00:11:56,767
I hope all of your inventions end up being marketed.

221
00:11:56,767 --> 00:11:59,067
It's all your fault!

222
00:11:59,067 --> 00:12:01,367
You're to blame for this.

223
00:12:01,367 --> 00:12:04,367
Right, you do monitor for him,

224
00:12:04,367 --> 00:12:06,067
representing the young generation, Ran!

225
00:12:06,067 --> 00:12:08,167
No, I'd rather not...

226
00:12:08,167 --> 00:12:10,967
Where's Conan?

227
00:12:10,967 --> 00:12:13,467
Conan! What are you doing?

228
00:12:13,467 --> 00:12:15,567
